FilterACutoffFrequency: Filter input frequencies range between 20.0f and 15000.0f.
FilterAResonance: Filter input resonances range between 0.5f and 10.0f.
FilterAOutputVolumeDB: Filter output dB range between 10.0f and -96.0f. Final Filter output is clamped to +6 dB, use positive values with caution.
FilterBCutoffFrequency: Filter input frequencies range between 20.0f and 15000.0f.
FilterBResonance: Filter input resonances range between 0.5f and 10.0f.
FilterBOutputVolumeDB: Filter output dB range between 10.0f and -96.0f. Final Filter output is clamped to +6 dB, use positive values with caution.
FilterMix: Filter Mix values range from -1.0f (Filter A) and 1.0f (Filter B).
